[I] Offers a series of D-Bus services to index filesystem resources

[T] Previously known as tracker-miners, is the indexer and search engine that
[T] powers the desktop search for core GNOME components. It stores data about
[T] user files structured by the Nepomuk definitions, features a tightly
[T] sandboxed metadata extractor, and provides facilities to alter file
[T] metadata.

[U] https://gitlab.gnome.org/GNOME/localsearch

